<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/css/website.css" />

    <title>Schemes</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/home"
          ><img
            src="https://www.clipartmax.com/png/middle/238-2386243_pills-comments-medicine-icon-png.png"
            alt="image not loading"
            id="pic"
        /></a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
          aria-controls="navbarNav"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
          <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/home">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link active" href="/schemes">Schemes</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/meds">Meds</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item-logout">
              <a href="/login" class="nav-link">Logout</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item-profile">
              <a href="/profile" class="nav-link"
                ><img
                  src="https://www.seekpng.com/png/detail/41-410093_circled-user-icon-user-profile-icon-png.png"
                  id="pp"
                  alt="na"
                />
                <%= profilename%></a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
      <!-- <h1>this is the schemes page</h1> -->
      <p>
        Access to quality healthcare is a fundamental right, but unfortunately, it's not always easy to navigate the complex healthcare system and understand the various government healthcare schemes available. However, a new feature aims to simplify this process by providing users with comprehensive information about various government healthcare schemes and assisting them in applying for them. With this feature, users can easily browse through the different schemes available, understand their eligibility criteria, and apply for the schemes that best suit their needs. This feature has the potential to make a significant impact on the lives of those who may not have been aware of the various healthcare schemes available to them, ultimately improving access to affordable and quality healthcare.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <% schemes.forEach(function(i){ %>
        <li class="schemes-item">
          <div class="scheme-text">
            Scheme Name: <%= i.name %> <br />
            Description: <%= i.data %> <br />
            Remuneration: <%= i.cost %>
          </div>
        </li>
        <br />
        <% }) %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
